# Rung 6 receipt, part 1: build the state a restart must bring back — a
# graph, a live content session on the focused node, and the sidecars
# (graph.json + browser_nodes.json + workbench.json + frame.json). Network-
# dependent (example.com); run on a FRESH profile; part 2 reuses it.
settle 30
key escape

open https://example.com/
settle 30
act Toggle live content
settle 30
assert content-live
act Save session
settle 5
capture 01_before_restart

log rung 6 restore receipt part 1 complete
